data.description: Impressive! This pristine 3-bedroom, 2.5 -bath home is nestled on .78 acres within a charming subdivision. It's USDA and FHA eligible, offering an added advantage. While there are no city taxes, its location provides easy access to the city of Cherryville, Shelby, and Gastonia. The modern open floor plan showcases granite countertops and elegant white cabinets.Kitchen also has a pantry for extra storage. Enjoy serene views in the spacious backyard. The second floor has updated flooring, a generous loft, and the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and large bathroom. With the laundry room and other bedrooms also upstairs, convenience is key. This move-in ready home awaits you!
